high_descs: Turn right, go straight, before the coffee table to right, go straight all the way, turn left, go straight to the wall past the brown chair. Go behind the brown chair and face the chair.
Take the remote control from the chair.
Turn left, go straight and to the right to the window, turn left to face the lamp.
Lift the remote control up and turn the lamp on.
anns.task_desc: Inspect a remote control near a lit lamp.

high_descs: Turn around, head towards the statue on the table, turn left towards the behind chair with the tv remote.
Pick up the tv remote on the chair.
Turn backwards to face the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a tv remote next to the light of a tall lamp.

high_descs: Turn right, then right again, cross the room, turn left to face the back of armchair.
Pick up remote control from seat of armchair.
Turn left, then left again to face lamp.
Use remote control to turn on the lamp
anns.task_desc: Turn on lamp with remote control
